                        "text": "Math.mulDiv(uint256,uint256,uint256) (../sb/VotacaoCondominio_F.sol#1880-1951) has bitwise-xor operator ^ instead of the exponentiation operator **: \n\t - inverse = (3 * denominator) ^ 2 (../sb/VotacaoCondominio_F.sol#1933)\n"
                    },
                    "ruleId": "slither_0_11_3_incorrect_exp"
