                        "text": "Math.invMod(uint256,uint256) (../sb/VotacaoCondominio_F.sol#1991-2037) performs a multiplication on the result of a division:\n\t- quotient = gcd / remainder (../sb/VotacaoCondominio_F.sol#2013)\n\t- (gcd,remainder) = (remainder,gcd - remainder * quotient) (../sb/VotacaoCondominio_F.sol#2015-2022)\n"
